latestIgtvVideos.title: How I keep hyperpigmentation at bay
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’ve always struggled with acne scarring and hyperpigmentation, and I still vividly remember when I would really get insecure about my skin during my teenage years. Even though there are a lot of factors that play into it, I soon realised how important it is to include a  sunscreen in my everyday skincare routine. But finding that perfect sunscreen was something I always struggled with, until I came across this amazing sunscreen from @reequil. (@reequil is a skincare brand that offers dermatologically tested products, developed by scientists and made from clinically proven ingredients. ) 

The sheer zinc tinted sunscreen is a 100% physical sunscreen, that is tinted to universally suit all skin tones, not leaving a white cast and provides a spf of 50! I’ve been using it over two weeks now, and it’s a sunscreen I’m definitely not looking to part away from soon! Make sure you watch the entire video to know more about it! 💜

You can check out the sheer zinc tinted sunscreen here : https://bit.ly/3jPlY7g 

#zincsunscreen #iamreequil #mineralsunscreen #physicalsunscreen #tintedsunscreen #universaltint #allskintones #reequil #sensitiveskin #allskintypes #ad

latestIgtvVideos.title: To anyone who needs to hear this
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Have you ever been in an emotional turmoil; not knowing whether to speak your mind, just because the labels, the constant judgement, the disagreements, the societal pressure scares you? I’ve been through that too, and there’s one thing I’ve learnt - the only thing that matters is yourself, your dream and an indomitable will. Don’t let anybody hold you back or stop yourself from following your passion. There’s nothing more powerful than investing in yourself. @pondsindia

#pondsindia #seewhathappens
